Encounter.title: Hallway
Encounter.Author: nobody
Encounter.IntroText: Its recess, and youre walking down the hall. You have new clothes on, your make-up looks good, and your hair is sitting perfectly which normally never happens. Its one of those rare good days, where you feel sexy and invincible. Down the hallway you see that Valdemar is coming your way; he looks so cool. You havent exchanged many words with him but you really want to catch his attention somehow. Valdemar breaks out in a big smile, and begins waving at you. You feel the rush and the excitement and you wave back at him. Suddenly, his expression changes and he looks at you a bit confused. You turn your head and notice a beautiful girl walking a few meters behind you. The rush of embarrassment starts streaming in, as you realize that he wasnt waving at you. What should you do?

Valdemar is looking down at you with his beautiful blue eyes. The butterflies start filling up, as you begin dancing closer and closer with him. He leans in tries to kiss you. Suddenly, a slide show begins on the projector showing photos from the party. The photos shows you and Valdemar dancing slowly and kissing. There is not just one picture but many! Encounter.IntroText: You just finished school and are on your way to the soccer pitches with Augusta. When you arrive at the pitch you see Johan talking with his father. Johan is putting on his soccer boots, getting ready for the match. His father is talking about how he should play. Encounter.title: Bus: Takeoff
Encounter.Author: nobody
Encounter.IntroText: You just arrived to the bus with your sleeping bag and pad ready for the intro trip. Youve got your pillow with you and your wearing your most relaxing clothes to make the bus-trip as comfortable as possible. Like all other 1. year students you have go on a intro trip to a cottage house. Every class is assigned a tutor, and your class has gotten Johan from 2.Y. Hes standing at the bus flirting with Olivia. You go over to drop your bags in the trunk of the bus. Johan comes over and take your bags You look tired, Rosa. Have you been up all night?. You look at him a bit confused

Reaction.ReactionText: He laughs and says "I see. A word of advice, you look better with make-up" and walks away. You feel a bit angry while thinking of what an idiot he is.
He says "Argh okay, you look nice though" and gives you a crooked smile.

He gives you a silly look and says "Seems like your not a morning person". You roll your eyes and walk away.

Encounter.title: Teacher's Pet
Encounter.Author: nobody
Encounter.IntroText: Youre sitting in class having math and youre listening to Mr. Nielsen explain something about integral calculus. He suddenly turns to you and asks you to go up to the whiteboard and solve the problem. You look around, feeling the stares of all your classmates. Thankfully youve done your homework, so you have no problem solving it. You quickly draw, explain and calculate the result. Mr Nielsen looks at you impressed and says to the class This is how its done, good job Rosa. On youre way back to your seat Olivia loudly says Someone has become the teachers pet she says with a smirk smile.

Option.OptionText: You give her an evil stare

Reaction.ReactionText: Olivia laughs even more seeing how it annoys you.
Olivia becomes quiet and looks down at the table

Option.OptionText: You ignore her
You say At least its better than being the teachers worst student

Reaction.ReactionText: Olivia looks surprised and a bit angry. She looks down at the table not knowing what to say.
She laughs and says "Like that will ever be true!"

Encounter.title: Valdemar asks Rosa out

Encounter.IntroText: The sun is shining, the birds are humming, and youre in a good mood. You finished school early and just said goodbye to your classmates. While walking with your bike away from the school you hear someone running up behind you. You turn around and see Valdemar coming towards you. He smiles and says Hi Rosa, Im glad I just catched you he says with a smile. He continues I wanted to ask what you are doing Friday? And if your perhaps would want to go to a concert with me? he looks at you intensely with his big blue eyes. You feel your heart beginning to race, as youre trying to look for words to say.
